long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Enhance your ChatGPT prompts with relevant web search results using web browsing.

This free extension integrates web results into your ChatGPT prompts, ensuring more precise and current conversations.

Additionally, it features a handy prompt management tool that lets you create and use custom prompt templates in ChatGPT, streamlining repetitive tasks.
